    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a mechanical masterpiece for the discerning purist. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully bulletproofed and rod bearings replaced as proactive maintenance. The atmospheric induction via six individual throttle bodies delivers razor-sharp throttle response up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is transmitted through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory 3.62:1 limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure long-term structural integrity. The chassis retains its original factory kinematics with no bushing deflection or play in the steering rack. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint is free of swirl marks and the undercarriage is exceptionally dry, showing no signs of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a collector-grade vehicle maintained to the highest mechanical standards.",
      "price": 43500.0,
