    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage by its sole original owner. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Step inside to a cabin that is indistinguishable from new. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any creasing or bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature and driver aid functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive service binder detailing every oil change and inspection performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. Equipped with fresh tires and all-original glass, this vehicle drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new machine. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that has been pampered since day one. Includes all original manuals, two master keys, and the original window sticker.",
