      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve meticulously babied it since day one, so it's in flawless shape inside and out. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. Come take a look\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed!",
